query:
update "user"
            set email = coalesce($1, "user".email),
                username = coalesce($2, "user".username),
                password_hash = coalesce($3, "user".password_hash),
                bio = coalesce($4, "user".bio),
                image = coalesce($5, "user".image)
            where user_id = $6
            returning email, username, bio, image
